Package com.alltrack.sdk

Class Alltrack

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alltrack.sdk.Alltrack
  • public class Alltrack
extends java.lang.Object
    The main interface to Alltrack. Use the methods of this class to tell Alltrack about the usage of your app. See the README for details.
    Since:
    11th November 2011
